description:
Tired of slow .NET Reflection API? This package will let you get rid of this overhead by replacing Reflection calls with much faster delegates.
      This package contains set of methods for creating delegates for accesing public, internal, protected and private members (fields, properties, indexers, methods and events) of types.
summary: Easy way for creating delegates to access types members. Much faster than Reflection.
